Project Name : Expense Tracker App

Project Description : Expense Tracker is an App were a user can keep track of his/her income and expenses, 
It also has a date, a chart that shows the transaction time and the flow. when the use inputs the type either income or expense, selects category, amount and date and click on the add; 
it then displays on the chart and on the transaction table.


Project Technical :
-HTML
-Javascript
-Css

